org.jamwiki.utils

Class WikiLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamwiki.utils.WikiLogger

  • public class WikiLogger
extends Object
    This class provides a wrapper around the SFL4J logging facade framework. A logging framework implementation will be chosen at runtime.
